{"number":18,"verseCount":47,"verses":[[1,["Now, behold, because of the thing which you, my servant Oliver Cowdery, have desired to know of me, I give unto you these words:"]],[2,["Behold, I have ",["manifested",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 6:24 (22–24)","dc-testament/dc/6.24"],"."]]]," unto you, by my Spirit in many instances, that the ",["things",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 9:4","dc-testament/dc/9.4"],"."]]]," which you have written are ",["true",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 6:17 (15–17)","dc-testament/dc/6.17"],"."]]],"; wherefore you know that they are true."]],[3,["And if you know that they are true, behold, I give unto you a commandment, that you ",["rely",["study-note-ref","a",[["Prov. 22:21","ot/prov/22.21"],"; ",["D&C 98:11","dc-testament/dc/98.11"],". ",["TG Dependability","tg/dependability"],"; ",["Guidance, Divine","tg/guidance-divine"],"; ",["Scriptures, Value of","tg/scriptures-value-of"],"."]]]," upon the things which are ",["written",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 18:30 (29–30)","dc-testament/dc/18.30"],"."]]],";"]],[4,["For in them are all things ",["written",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 20:9 (8–11)","dc-testament/dc/20.9"],"; ",["39:11","dc-testament/dc/39.11"],"; ",["68:1","dc-testament/dc/68.1"],". ",["TG Gospel","tg/gospel"],"."]]]," concerning the foundation of my church, my gospel, and my ",["rock",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 6:34","dc-testament/dc/6.34"],"; ",["10:69","dc-testament/dc/10.69"],"; ",["11:16 (16, 24)","dc-testament/dc/11.16"],"; ",["33:13","dc-testament/dc/33.13"],"."]]],"."]],[5,["Wherefore, if you shall build up my ",["church",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Church","tg/church"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Head of the Church","tg/jesus-christ-head-of-the-church"],"."]]],", upon the foundation of my gospel and my ",["rock",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Rock","tg/rock"],"."]]],", the ",["gates",["study-note-ref","c",[["Matt. 16:18","nt/matt/16.18"],"; ",["D&C 10:69","dc-testament/dc/10.69"],"."]]]," of hell shall not prevail against you."]],[6,["Behold, the ",["world",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG World","tg/world"],"."]]]," is ",["ripening",["study-note-ref","b",[["Rev. 14:15","nt/rev/14.15"],"."]]]," in iniquity; and it must needs be that the children of men are stirred up unto repentance, both the ",["Gentiles",["study-note-ref","c",[["1 Ne. 13:42","bofm/1-ne/13.42"],"; ",["D&C 18:26","dc-testament/dc/18.26"],"; ",["19:27","dc-testament/dc/19.27"],"; ",["21:12","dc-testament/dc/21.12"],"; ",["90:9 (8–9)","dc-testament/dc/90.9"],"; ",["107:33","dc-testament/dc/107.33"],"; ",["112:4","dc-testament/dc/112.4"],". ",["TG Gentiles","tg/gentiles"],"; ",["Israel, Restoration of","tg/israel-restoration-of"],"; ",["Missionary Work","tg/missionary-work"],"."]]]," and also the house of Israel."]],[7,["Wherefore, as thou hast been ",["baptized",["study-note-ref","a",[["JS—H 1:71 (70–71)","pgp/js-h/1.71"],"."]]]," by the hands of my servant Joseph Smith, Jun., according to that which I have commanded him, he hath fulfilled the thing which I commanded him."]],[8,["And now, marvel not that I have ",["called",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 9:12","dc-testament/dc/9.12"],"."]]]," him unto mine own purpose, ",["",29],"which purpose is known in me; wherefore, if he shall be ",["diligent",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Diligence","tg/diligence"],"."]]]," in keeping my commandments he shall be ",["blessed",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Blessing","tg/blessing"],"."]]]," unto eternal life; and his name is ",["Joseph",["study-note-ref","d",[["2 Ne. 3:15 (14–15)","bofm/2-ne/3.15"],". ",["TG Joseph Smith","tg/joseph-smith"],"."]]],"."]],[9,["And now, Oliver Cowdery, I speak unto you, and also unto David Whitmer, by the way of commandment; for, behold, I ",["command",["study-note-ref","a",[["Acts 17:30","nt/acts/17.30"],"."]]]," all men everywhere to repent, and I speak unto you, even as unto Paul mine ",["apostle",["study-note-ref","b",[["Rom. 1:1","nt/rom/1.1"],"."]]],", for you are called even with that same calling with which he was called."]],[10,["Remember the ",["worth",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 43:4","ot/isa/43.4"],". ",["TG Life, Sanctity of","tg/life-sanctity-of"],"; ",["Worth of Souls","tg/worth-of-souls"],"."]]]," of ",["souls",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Soul","tg/soul"],"."]]]," is great in the sight of God;"]],[11,["For, behold, the Lord your ",["Redeemer",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Redeemer","tg/jesus-christ-redeemer"],"."]]]," suffered ",["death",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Death","tg/death"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Death of","tg/jesus-christ-death-of"],"."]]]," in the flesh; wherefore he ",["suffered",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Redemption","tg/redemption"],"; ",["Self-Sacrifice","tg/self-sacrifice"],"."]]]," the ",["pain",["study-note-ref","d",[["Isa. 53:4 (4–5)","ot/isa/53.4"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through","tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"],"; ",["Pain","tg/pain"],"."]]]," of all men, that all men might repent and ",["come",["study-note-ref","e",[["John 12:32","nt/john/12.32"],"."]]]," unto him."]],[12,["And he hath ",["risen",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Resurrection","tg/jesus-christ-resurrection"],"."]]]," again from the dead, that he might bring all men unto him, on conditions of ",["repentance",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 19:4 (4–18)","dc-testament/dc/19.4"],"."]]],"."]],[13,["And how great is his ",["joy",["study-note-ref","a",[["Luke 15:7","nt/luke/15.7"],"."]]]," in the ",["soul",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Worth of Souls","tg/worth-of-souls"],"."]]]," that ",["repenteth",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Repent","tg/repent"],"."]]],"!"]],[14,["Wherefore, you are called to ",["cry",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 6:9","dc-testament/dc/6.9"],"; ",["34:6","dc-testament/dc/34.6"],"; ",["63:57","dc-testament/dc/63.57"],"."]]]," repentance unto this people."]],[15,["And if it so be that you should labor all your days in crying repentance unto this people, and bring, save it be one ",["soul",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Missionary Work","tg/missionary-work"],"; ",["Worth of Souls","tg/worth-of-souls"],"."]]]," unto me, how great shall be your joy with him in the kingdom of my Father!"]],[16,["And now, if your joy will be great with one soul that you have brought unto me into the ",["kingdom",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Kingdom of God, in Heaven","tg/kingdom-of-god-in-heaven"],"."]]]," of my Father, how great will be your ",["joy",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 4:36","nt/john/4.36"],"; ",["1 Thes. 3:9","nt/1-thes/3.9"],"; ",["Alma 26:11 (11–13)","bofm/alma/26.11"],"; ",["D&C 50:22 (17–22)","dc-testament/dc/50.22"],". ",["TG Joy","tg/joy"],"."]]]," if you should bring many ",["souls",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Conversion","tg/conversion"],"."]]]," unto me!"]],[17,["Behold, you have my gospel before you, and my rock, and my ",["salvation",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Rock","tg/rock"],"; ",["Salvation","tg/salvation"],"."]]],"."]],[18,[["Ask",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Prayer","tg/prayer"],"."]]]," the Father in my ",["name",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 15:16","nt/john/15.16"],"."]]]," in faith, believing that you shall receive, and you shall have the Holy Ghost, which manifesteth all things which are ",["expedient",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 88:64 (63–65)","dc-testament/dc/88.64"],"."]]]," unto the children of men."]],[19,["And if you have not ",["faith",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Faith","tg/faith"],"."]]],", ",["hope",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Hope","tg/hope"],"."]]],", and ",["charity",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Charity","tg/charity"],"."]]],", you can do nothing."]],[20,[["Contend",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Tim. 2:24 (23–24)","nt/2-tim/2.24"],"; ",["3 Ne. 11:29 (29–30)","bofm/3-ne/11.29"],"."]]]," against no church, save it be the ",["church of the devil",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Devil, Church of","tg/devil-church-of"],"."]]],"."]],[21,["Take upon you the ",["name",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Taking the Name of","tg/jesus-christ-taking-the-name-of"],"."]]]," of Christ, and ",["speak",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Cor. 4:13","nt/2-cor/4.13"],"; ",["D&C 100:7 (5–8)","dc-testament/dc/100.7"],"."]]]," the truth in ",["soberness",["study-note-ref","c",[["Rom. 12:3","nt/rom/12.3"],"; ",["D&C 43:35","dc-testament/dc/43.35"],"."]]],"."]],[22,["And as many as repent and are ",["baptized",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Baptism, Essential","tg/baptism-essential"],"."]]]," in my name, which is Jesus Christ, and ",["endure",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Perseverance","tg/perseverance"],"; ",["Steadfastness","tg/steadfastness"],"."]]]," to the end, the same shall be saved."]],[23,["Behold, Jesus Christ is the ",["name",["study-note-ref","a",[["Mal. 1:11","ot/mal/1.11"],"; ",["Acts 4:12","nt/acts/4.12"],"."]]]," which is given of the Father, and there is none other name given whereby man can be ",["saved",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through","tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Savior","tg/jesus-christ-savior"],"; ",["Salvation","tg/salvation"],"; ",["Salvation, Plan of","tg/salvation-plan-of"],"."]]],";"]],[24,["Wherefore, all men must take upon them the ",["name",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Taking the Name of","tg/jesus-christ-taking-the-name-of"],"."]]]," which is given of the Father, for in that name shall they be called at the last day;"]],[25,["Wherefore, if they ",["know not",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Ignorance","tg/ignorance"],"."]]]," the ",["name",["study-note-ref","b",[["Mosiah 5:12 (9–14)","bofm/mosiah/5.12"],"."]]]," by which they are called, they cannot have place in the ",["kingdom",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Kingdom of God, in Heaven","tg/kingdom-of-god-in-heaven"],"."]]]," of my Father."]],[26,["And now, behold, there are others who are ",["called",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Authority","tg/authority"],"."]]]," to declare my gospel, both unto ",["Gentile",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Ne. 13:42","bofm/1-ne/13.42"],"; ",["D&C 18:6","dc-testament/dc/18.6"],"; ",["19:27","dc-testament/dc/19.27"],"; ",["21:12","dc-testament/dc/21.12"],"; ",["90:9 (8–9)","dc-testament/dc/90.9"],"; ",["107:33","dc-testament/dc/107.33"],"; ",["112:4","dc-testament/dc/112.4"],"."]]]," and unto Jew;"]],[27,["Yea, even twelve; and the ",["Twelve",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Apostles","tg/apostles"],"."]]]," shall be my disciples, and they shall take upon them my name; and the Twelve are they who shall desire to take upon them my ",["name",["study-note-ref","b",[["Jer. 15:16","ot/jer/15.16"],"; ",["D&C 27:12","dc-testament/dc/27.12"],"."]]]," with full purpose of heart."]],[28,["And if they desire to take upon them my name with full purpose of heart, they are called to go into all the ",["world",["study-note-ref","a",[["Mark 16:15 (15–16)","nt/mark/16.15"],"."]]]," to preach my ",["gospel",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Gospel","tg/gospel"],"."]]]," unto ",["every creature",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 1:2 (2, 34–35)","dc-testament/dc/1.2"],"; ",["39:15","dc-testament/dc/39.15"],"; ",["42:58","dc-testament/dc/42.58"],"."]]],"."]],[29,["And they are they who are ordained of me to ",["baptize",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 4:2 (1–2)","nt/john/4.2"],"; ",["3 Ne. 11:22 (21–22)","bofm/3-ne/11.22"],"; ",["12:1","bofm/3-ne/12.1"],"; ",["D&C 20:38","dc-testament/dc/20.38"],"."]]]," in my name, according to that which is written;"]],[30,["And you have that which is written before you; wherefore, you must perform it ",["according",["study-note-ref","a",[["3 Ne. 11:22 (22–28)","bofm/3-ne/11.22"],"; ",["D&C 20:72 (72–74)","dc-testament/dc/20.72"],"."]]]," to the words which are ",["written",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 18:3 (3–4)","dc-testament/dc/18.3"],"."]]],"."]],[31,["And now I speak unto you, the ",["Twelve",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 107:23 (23–39)","dc-testament/dc/107.23"],"."]]],"—Behold, my grace is sufficient for you; you must walk uprightly before me and sin not."]],[32,["And, behold, you are they who are ordained of me to ",["ordain",["study-note-ref","a",[["Moro. 3:4 (1–4)","bofm/moro/3.4"],"; ",["D&C 20:39 (39, 60)","dc-testament/dc/20.39"],"; ",["107:58","dc-testament/dc/107.58"],". ",["TG Priesthood, Ordination","tg/priesthood-ordination"],"."]]]," priests and teachers; to declare my gospel, ",["according",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Pet. 1:21","nt/2-pet/1.21"],"; ",["D&C 68:3 (3–4)","dc-testament/dc/68.3"],"."]]]," to the power of the Holy Ghost which is in you, and according to the ",["callings",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 20:27","dc-testament/dc/20.27"],"."]]]," and gifts of God unto men;"]],[33,["And I, Jesus Christ, your Lord and your God, have spoken it."]],[34,["These ",["words",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Scriptures, Value of","tg/scriptures-value-of"],"."]]]," are not of men nor of man, but of me; wherefore, you shall testify they are of me and not of man;"]],[35,["For it is my ",["voice",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 1:38","dc-testament/dc/1.38"],". ",["TG Revelation","tg/revelation"],"."]]]," which speaketh them unto you; for they are given by my Spirit unto you, and by my power you can read them one to another; and save it were by my power you could not have them;"]],[36,["Wherefore, you can ",["testify",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Testimony","tg/testimony"],"."]]]," that you have ",["heard",["study-note-ref","b",[["Ex. 19:9 (7–13)","ot/ex/19.9"],"."]]]," my voice, and know my words."]],[37,["And now, behold, I give unto you, Oliver Cowdery, and also unto David Whitmer, that you shall search out the Twelve, who shall have the desires of which I have spoken;"]],[38,["And by their ",["desires",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Motivations","tg/motivations"],"."]]]," and their ",["works",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Good Works","tg/good-works"],"."]]]," you shall know them."]],[39,["And when you have found them you shall show these things unto them."]],[40,["And you shall fall down and ",["worship",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Worship","tg/worship"],"."]]]," the Father in my ",["name",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Kgs. 8:29","ot/1-kgs/8.29"],". ",["TG Name","tg/name"],"."]]],"."]],[41,["And you must preach unto the world, saying: You must ",["repent",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Baptism, Essential","tg/baptism-essential"],"; ",["Repent","tg/repent"],"."]]]," and be baptized, in the name of Jesus Christ;"]],[42,["For all men must repent and be baptized, and not only men, but women, and ",["children",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Children","tg/children"],"; ",["Family, Children, Duties of","tg/family-children-duties-of"],"."]]]," who have arrived at the years of ",["accountability",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 20:71","dc-testament/dc/20.71"],"; ",["29:47","dc-testament/dc/29.47"],"; ",["68:25 (25–27)","dc-testament/dc/68.25"],"."]]],"."]],[43,["And now, after that you have received this, you must keep my ",["commandments",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Commandments of God","tg/commandments-of-god"],"."]]]," in all things;"]],[44,["And by your hands I will work a ",["marvelous work",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 29:14","ot/isa/29.14"],"; ",["D&C 4:1","dc-testament/dc/4.1"],"; ",["6:1","dc-testament/dc/6.1"],"."]]]," among the ",["",31],"children of men, unto the ",["convincing",["study-note-ref","b",[["Job 13:23 (23–28)","ot/job/13.23"],"; ",["Alma 12:1","bofm/alma/12.1"],"; ",["36:17 (12–19)","bofm/alma/36.17"],"; ",["62:45","bofm/alma/62.45"],"; ",["D&C 6:11","dc-testament/dc/6.11"],"."]]]," of many of their sins, that they may come unto repentance, and that they may come unto the kingdom of my Father."]],[45,["Wherefore, the blessings which I give unto you are ",["above",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 76:92","dc-testament/dc/76.92"],"; ",["84:38 (35–38)","dc-testament/dc/84.38"],"."]]]," all things."]],[46,["And after that you have received this, if you ",["keep",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Pet. 4:17 (17–18)","nt/1-pet/4.17"],"; ",["D&C 82:3","dc-testament/dc/82.3"],"."]]]," not my commandments you cannot be saved in the kingdom of my Father."]],[47,["Behold, I, Jesus Christ, your Lord and your God, and your ",["Redeemer",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Redeemer","tg/jesus-christ-redeemer"],"."]]],", by the ",["power",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Power of","tg/jesus-christ-power-of"],"."]]]," of my Spirit have spoken it. Amen."]]],"volume":"dc"}